  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110099002028\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110099002028\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong>&#65279;저작근들 (음식을 씹을 때 사용하는 근육들)</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101214_60/isuhani_12923169287147bQX3_JPEG/imagesCAO7SBZR.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"265\" height=\"190\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20101214_60/isuhani_12923169287147bQX3_JPEG/imagesCAO7SBZR.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A26972AC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101214_60/isuhani_12923169287147bQX3_JPEG/imagesCAO7SBZR.jpg?type=w3\"></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 턱관절에 문제가 있을 때도 두통이 자주 생기겠죠!</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 두통이 있으면서 턱관절에 문제가 있는 분은 턱관절 교정까지 해야합니다. </strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong>승모근과 어깨쪽 근육들</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101214_171/isuhani_1292317006809SBthy_JPEG/imagesCAQG0HZQ.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"155\" height=\"178\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20101214_171/isuhani_1292317006809SBthy_JPEG/imagesCAQG0HZQ.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A26972AC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101214_171/isuhani_1292317006809SBthy_JPEG/imagesCAQG0HZQ.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 어깨가 늘 무겁고 뭉쳐있는 분들이 두통이 있으면 어깨도 같이 치료해야겠죠.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong>뒷골, 목뼈 위쪽에 있는 작은 근육들</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101214_94/isuhani_1292317112081B15Kf_JPEG/%C8%C4%B5%CE%C7%CF%B1%D9.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"274\" height=\"184\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20101214_94/isuhani_1292317112081B15Kf_JPEG/%C8%C4%B5%CE%C7%CF%B1%D9.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A26972AC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101214_94/isuhani_1292317112081B15Kf_JPEG/%C8%C4%B5%CE%C7%CF%B1%D9.jpg?type=w3\"></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 뒷골이 땡겨요</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 뒷골이 뻐근해요</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 라는 얘기 많이 하죠? 그런경우 경추 1,2번 쪽에 문제가 있으면 같이 치료해야해요</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 필요하면 교정도 같이 해줘야 하지요. </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">목의 앞쪽 근육들</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101214_197/isuhani_12923172266368m4Ba_JPEG/imagesCAUME0PV.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"251\" height=\"201\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"20101214_197/isuhani_12923172266368m4Ba_JPEG/imagesCAUME0PV.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A26972AC')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20101214_197/isuhani_12923172266368m4Ba_JPEG/imagesCAUME0PV.jpg?type=w3\"></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 어지럽고 머리아플때, 교통사고 후 두통에 많이 영향을 줘요</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">이 외에도 많아요. 목 주변에 근육이 수십개가 넘거든요.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
